Yeah, this.  Didn&#x27;t realize people actually saw this as an issue worthy of worrying about.<p>The Matasano Crypto Challenges I did way back when were in Go and the ones involving ECB were just done as for loops over the standard library AES Decrypt/Encrypt methods, something like this:<p><pre><code>  for i := 0; i < blockCount; i++ {
    start := i * blockLength
    end := start + blockLength
    aes.Decrypt(decryptBuffer, input[start:end])
    output = append(output, decryptBuffer) 
  }</code></pre>
